<h1 id="setup-impairment-accounting-common-parameters-and-posting-profile" sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="28">Setup impairment accounting common parameters and posting profile</h1>


<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">Use this task to learn how to define impairment accounting common parameters and posting profiles.</p>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">To complete this task, the Fixed Assets configuration key must be selected.</p>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">This procedure uses the JPMF demo company data.</p>
<h2 id="set-up-impairment-parameters" sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="43">Set up impairment parameters</h2>
<ol sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Go to Fixed assets &gt; Setup &gt; Fixed assets parameters.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Expand the Impairment management section.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">In the Warning period (in months) field, enter a number.
<ul sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Example: 6 months</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Click the Number sequences tab. Confirm the following Number sequence codes are set up:</li>
</ol>
<ul sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49">Document ID for impairment</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Impairment test ID</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">Cash generating unit number</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="set-up-posting-profile" sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">Set up posting profile</h2>
<ol sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Go to Fixed assets &gt; Setup &gt; Fixed asset posting profiles.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">Click Edit.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="56">Expand the Impairment management section.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57">Click Add.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">In the Book field, type a value.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">In the Groupings field, select an option.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">In the Fixed asset number field, type a value.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">In the Main account field, specify the desired values.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">In the Offset account field, specify the desired values.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/impairment-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">Click Save.</li>
</ol>
</article>
